<BES xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="BES.xsd">
	<Fixlet>
		<Title>MS02-006: SNMP Service Unchecked Buffer in Windows 95</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
Microsoft has released a security bulletin announcing an unchecked buffer vulnerability in the Microsoft Simple Network Management Protocol for Windows 95. According to Microsoft, a buffer overrun is present in virtually all implementations of this service which can be exploited by an attacker to cause a denial of service. In addition, it is possible that the attacker could cause code to run on the system in LocalSystem context, potentially providing the ability to take any desired action on the system. Microsoft recommends disabling SNMP services on affected computers until it releases a patch for Windows 95.<BR><BR><b>Note:</b> This Fixlet message does not have a default action. For more information on default actions, see BigFix KB #474.
]]></Description>
		<Relevance>(if( name of operating system starts with "Win" ) then platform id of operating system != 3 else false) AND (if exists property "in proxy agent context" then ( not in proxy agent context ) else true )</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(language of version block of file "kernel32.dll" of system folder contains "English") OR (exists value of key "HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Nls\MUILanguages" of registry)</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKLM\Software\Wow6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion" whose (exists value "ProductId" of it OR exists value "CommonFilesDir" of it) of registry AND not exists values "PROCESSOR_ARCHITECTURE" whose (it as string as lowercase = "ia64") of keys "HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager\Environment" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>name of operating system is "Win95"</Relevance>
		<Relevance>exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\SNMP" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(not exists key "ESRemovedFixlets" of key "HKLM\Software\BigFix\EnterpriseClient" of registry) OR (not exists value "200611" of key "HKLM\Software\BigFix\EnterpriseClient\ESRemovedFixlets" of registry) OR (value "200611" of key "HKLM\Software\BigFix\EnterpriseClient\ESRemovedFixlets" of registry ) != 1</Relevance>
